{"tid":1848831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反了反了 公安禁農村佬set rb防武漢人 大批支那人暴動留言鬧爆","createTime":"2020-01-28T16:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T08:15:14.000Z","uid":104470,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"251a29ce9f845de354397eca13fa18ac46024e53","tid":1848831,"uid":104470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"#未經批准擅自斷路將依法處置#<br />\n【公安部：未經批准擅自斷路等行為將依法處置】<br />\n1月28日，公安部部長趙克志在應對新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情工作領導小組第一次會議上要求，要全力配合有關部門做好疫情監測、排查、預警，以及感染患者收治和疑似病例及其密切接觸者的核查隔離等工作，切實做到早發現、早報告、早隔離、早治療，堅決防止疫情擴散蔓延。開闢綠色通道，優先保障救護車輛、防疫車輛和運送醫護人員、藥品器械、民生物資等車輛通行。<span style=\"color: red;\">對未經批准擅自設卡攔截、斷路阻斷交通等違法行為，依法穩妥處置，維護正常交通秩序。</span>（新京報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1649173367/4465759915044469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F1649173367%2F4465759915044469&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=fc3f8632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/1649173367/4465759915044469</a><br />\n<br />\n大批支那人暴動留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtfNap0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtfNap0.png&h=86c2b8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NFA3K1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NFA3K1.png&h=3434b914&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcQ5GwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcQ5GwH.png&h=9d4a23b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HtyQp4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HtyQp4.png&h=52f3015b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGKqGwM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGKqGwM.png&h=de1128f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid